    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Discover Love, Challenge Gravity</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Where love defies the laws of gravity! Join Mimo and Mimi, two souls separated by cosmic fears and challenges. Embark on an epic journey through inverted realms, solving puzzles, and overcoming obstacles in the quest for reconciliation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266320/extras/852f1307793f2f876a4629a641ef1a6d.avif?t=1728586335\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266320/extras_big/852f1307793f2f876a4629a641ef1a6d.avif?t=1728586335 width=800 height=454 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What would you do if you had a second chance?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not everybody has this kind of luck, but Mimo and Mimi do. Will they use this opportunity to stay together this time?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266320/extras/a9745857ec8dcd564a5087e5f59e4d9c.avif?t=1728586335\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266320/extras_big/a9745857ec8dcd564a5087e5f59e4d9c.avif?t=1728586335 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique Puzzles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rotate the map, turn it upside down, and control each character in its perspective. Everything one does will affect the other's side creating challenging and unique puzzles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266320/extras/a3ce3902c42be3a936a1a16f882636ad.avif?t=1728586335\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266320/extras_big/a3ce3902c42be3a936a1a16f882636ad.avif?t=1728586335 width=800 height=490 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Face fears</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face incredible final bosses that will change the course of the level.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266320/extras/7541852946d8ae1983267506ba3f3ba2.avif?t=1728586335\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266320/extras_big/7541852946d8ae1983267506ba3f3ba2.avif?t=1728586335 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
